@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC037 ManageMasterData

actor "Admin" as Actor
boundary "AdminUI" as UI
control "MasterDataController" as Controller
entity "MasterDataDB" as Entity

Actor -> UI : 1. Chọn danh mục (Category/Unit) & Thêm/Sửa/Xóa
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. executeCRUD(action, data)
activate Controller
Controller -> Entity : 3. updateDatabase(action, data)
activate Entity
Entity --> Controller : 4. success
deactivate Entity
Controller --> UI : 5. Thông báo thay đổi thành công
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 6. Làm mới danh sách Master Data hiển thị
deactivate UI
@enduml
